body.description: SHARECOOK Silverware Set Durable and simple to maintain, this 40-piece silverware set is ideal for the daily rigors of your kitchen. The forks, spoons and knives are ergonomically crafted for a comfortable dining experience. - Smoothened edges and ergonomic handles. - Complete silverware set for full service. - Shining look with simple detailing. - Dishwasher safe for hassle-free cleaning. All about Durability Our silverware are crafted from good quality 18/0 stainless steel; You’ll never have to worry about the knives struggling to cut, the spoons bending as you chow away, or the prongs of the forks curling out of shape like others do. Simple Classic Designs Make your dining table stand out with a silverware set that is eye-catching without being visually overpowering. Inspired by minimalist elegance, the stainless steel silverware set is designed to beautifully blend into any setting. No cheap-looking gaudy detailing here. Just simple design with clean lines that come off as timeless. Maintenance Made Easy No struggling with pastes and sprays to polish your silverware set. This premium silverware set doesn’t need all that effort to keep it in great condition. The lovely look remains in beautifully shape without your intervention, and with the unique silverware set being dishwasher safe, clean-up will be a breeze! Complement your Dining with an Effortlessly Elegant Silverware Set Upgrade your silverware set with stainless steel silverware strong enough to withstand heavy daily use and elegant enough to complement the fanciest of dinners. Blending premium materials with experienced craftsmanship and timeless detailing,SHARECOOK stainless steel silverware set treats you to impressive durability, eye-catching aesthetics, and convenient functionality.
